org.apache.drill.exec.physical.impl.scan.project.projSet

Class TestProjectionSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.drill.test.BaseTest
      • org.apache.drill.exec.physical.impl.scan.project.projSet.TestProjectionSet

  • public class TestProjectionSet
extends BaseTest
    Test the projection set used by the result set loader as columns are added. The projection set combines information from the SELECT (project) list, from an optional provided schema, and from an optional type converter to decide whether a particular new column should be projected or not, and if so, is any type conversion is needed.

    The code and tests here keep the result set loader simple: it just asks a question about projection and gets an answer, the complexity of projection should be fully tested here, then just sanity tested in the result set loader.
